{"tid":1905324,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Apple 向湖北、温州員工送上「抗疫包」　口罩之外更有 iPad","createTime":"2020-03-01T07:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T07:38:37.000Z","uid":104138,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51dbcef92dc875a1e0f2c38a11203f9f7ef633b7","tid":1905324,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:37:58.000Z","msg":"面對疫情，Apple 沒有忘記湖北、温州員工。近日 Apple 向因封城而被「隔離」的員工送上「祝福包」，當中除了有口罩、消毒物資、食物、茶包等東西，更大方送出 iPad 10.2 吋，希望透過送上 iPad，能幫助他們的孩子在網上學習，讓他們能渡過這段困難的日子。<br />\n<br />\n不少分析也指出，iPad 的需求因疫情影響而大幅提高，很多人也因為要家中工作或讓小孩家中學習而購買 iPad。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/03/01/apple-china-bag-to-empolyee/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F03%2F01%2Fapple-china-bag-to-empolyee%2F&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGov%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=c42c40fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/03/01/apple-china-bag-to-empolyee/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又唔見tim cook送iPad比受澳洲大火影響既家庭？"},{"pid":"d5b36688926ddf6bc0852ac9699a868dc3aa577e","tid":1905324,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:38:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「為左手足，我地一定要鸁！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[真核彈，攬炒好唔好？] 立法會過半，就可以解散政府，唔洗分組點票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1905314/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1905314/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n一堆惡法排緊隊上立法會，連登仔：攬炒，唔好選。<br />\n辱警罪 禁蒙面 國歌法 23條 網絡23 網絡實名 禁罷工 拆關口 改議規<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1899255/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1899255/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7c29c2514446c01d3b035451d5ec86e6be75f548","tid":1905324,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}